Dependencies
------------
 - libgtk-3.0-dev
 - libgtksourceview-3.0-dev
 - libgranite
 - libgconf-2.0-dev
 - libzeitgeist-1.0

Testing and installation
------------------------
$ mkdir build
$ cd build/
$ cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr ..
$ make
$ sudo make install
$ ./src/scratch-text-editor

Thanks!
